2.00	Antigona	Antigona	Antigona is an opera in three acts in Italian by the composer Tommaso Traetta. The libretto, by Marco Coltellini, is based on the tragedy Antigone by Sophocles.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cb/Tommaso_Traetta_engraving.jpg/220px-Tommaso_Traetta_engraving.jpg
